There were Northern and Southern Yankees, and Yankees proper, some with ladies. some by themselves.

abstract: The Nashville (Tenn.) Union gives the following particulars of a destructive fire which occurred in that city on the 9th. A tire broke out in the extensive bedstead manufactory of Mr. J. W.
